lude them from `impact_estimates`.\n\n**Execution Context:**\n- Output directory: /home/AMD/khoffmey/dev/TraceLens/evals/unit_tests_comparative/test06_conv_gap_exceeds_roofline/analysis_output_ref\n- Command prefix: read `/home/AMD/khoffmey/dev/TraceLens/evals/unit_tests_comparative/test06_conv_gap_exceeds_roofline/analysis_output_ref/cache/cmd_prefix.txt` — contains a template\n  with `{CMD}` placeholder; substitute `{CMD}` with the actual command\n\nRead and follow the FULL instructions in:\n  TraceLens/AgenticMode/Standalone/.cursor/agents/convolution-analyzer.md\n\n- Category: convolution\n- Input files: category_data/convolution_ops.csv, metadata/convolution_metadata.json,\n  category_data/conv_fwd_tree_data.json (if available)\n- Output file: category_findings/convolution_findings.md\n\nExecute every step in the agent file. Return \"DONE\" when complete.","subagentType":{"custom":{"name":"convolution-analyzer"}},"model":"composer-2-fast","agentId":"7dcb387b-f363-4001-b7b0-fb84781fb3d5","attachments":[],"mode":"TASK_MODE_UNSPECIFIED","respondingToMessageIds":[]}}},"model_call_id":"f3657724-9c30-457f-812a-5c07f7300673-15-nwiz","session_id":"1415083f-2a1f-4988-abe9-6e5ae135413f","timestamp_ms":1777504659287}
