gory CSVs and metrics\n- `metadata/` — model info and platform metadata","session_id":"1415083f-2a1f-4988-abe9-6e5ae135413f","request_id":"f3657724-9c30-457f-812a-5c07f7300673","usage":{"inputTokens":42,"outputTokens":11032,"cacheReadTokens":1992191,"cacheWriteTokens":73458}}
